411
00:36:05,656 --> 00:36:07,299
Do que tive de fazer...

412
00:36:08,631 --> 00:36:10,634
- Fuja.
- Carol, atire.

413
00:36:10,636 --> 00:36:12,000
Vá em frente.

414
00:36:12,317 --> 00:36:14,441
Eu já perdi tudo mesmo.

415
00:36:18,178 --> 00:36:19,634
<i>Paula?</i>

416
00:36:20,412 --> 00:36:21,726
<i>Paula?</i>

417
00:36:24,297 --> 00:36:25,949
<i>Molly?</i>

418
00:36:37,291 --> 00:36:39,629
